<div id="reddit-ad-costs-by-ad-type"></div>
<h2>Reddit ad costs by ad type</h2>
<p>Now that you have a feel for how Reddit ad costs compare to other social media platforms, let‚Äôs go a layer deeper and take a look at average costs by ad type. There are several different Reddit ad types, and their names are always evolving, but this should give you a general idea of ad formats and prices:</p>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><b>Ad type</b></td>
<td><b>CPM range</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Image ads</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">$0.50 &#8211; $12</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Video ads</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">$2 &#8211; $20</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Carousel Ads</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">$6 &#8211; $18</span></td>
</tr>
