</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>As you can see, Takeover ads have the highest CPMs as they are a premium placement.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Note that pricing fluctuates based on audience size, targeting options, and competition. More on this in a bit.</span></p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f6d1.png" alt="üõë" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <strong>Before you advertise on Reddit, make sure you‚Äôre targeting the right audience!</strong> Learn <a href="https://gannett.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/teams/ContentSEOTeam/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7BF8A25C52-3731-4AAB-BEBE-40069BB61306%7D&amp;file=In-content%20CIDs.xlsx&amp;action=default&amp;mobileredirect=true">How to Find Your Target Audience</a></p>
<div id="reddit-ad-costs-vs-other-platforms"></div>
<h2>Reddit ad costs vs. other platforms</h2>
<p>Below are Reddit CPMs compared to other <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/07/18/social-media-advertising">social media advertising</a> platforms, including Facebook, Twitter/X, and LinkedIn:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/reddit-advertising-cost-wordstream-cpm-vs-graph.webp" alt="Reddit advertising cost - Graph of various social ad platform CPMs" width="936" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93200 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/reddit-advertising-cost-wordstream-cpm-vs-graph.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/reddit-advertising-cost-wordstream-cpm-vs-graph-480x308.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
