<ul>
<li>American History Month</li>
<li>American Heart Month (heart disease)</li>
<li>Bake for Family Fun Month</li>
<li>Black History Month</li>
<li>Cancer Prevention Month</li>
<li>Children&#8217;s Dental Health Month</li>
<li>Embroidery Month</li>
<li>Free and Open-Source Software Month</li>
<li>Library Lover‚Äôs Month</li>
<li>Self-Check Month</li>
<li>Teen Dating Violence Awareness Month</li>
<li>Wedding Month</li>
</ul>
<p>Some of these are general while others are highly specific, so depending on your business, your trade, or your <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/niche-markets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">niche</a>, you may or may not be able to apply these to your <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/february-social-media-holidays-and-ideas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">February social media and marketing campaigns </a>(National Embroidery Month isn‚Äôt exactly versatile, for example).</p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f4a1.png" alt="üí°" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <strong>Want marketing ideas for every month of the year?</strong> Free guide &gt;&gt; <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/resources/marketing-calendar?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Guide_2025MarketingCalendar_Download&amp;itm_source=wordstream&amp;itm_medium=blog&amp;itm_campaign=incontent_links">The Mega Must-Have Marketing Calendar</a></p>
