<ul>
<li><strong>Known:</strong> Groundhog Day, <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/presidents-day-marketing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">President&#8217;s Day</a>, Valentine&#8217;s Day (<a href="/blog/ws/2021/01/25/valentines-day-marketing-ideas">Valentine&#8217;s Day marketing ideas here,</a> and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/02/04/valentines-day-messages-clients">Valentine&#8217;s Day Messages here</a>), Galentine&#8217;s Day.</li>
