<li><strong>Meaningful:</strong> Freedom Day, Girls and Women in Sports Day, Wear Red Day, Safer Internet Day, <span style="font-weight: 400;">Random Acts of Kindness Day, Shut-In Visitation Day, Set a Good Example Day, Skip the Straw Day.</span></li>
<li><strong>Industry-specific:</strong> Toothache Day, Dog Biscuit Day, Love Your Pet Day, Spay Day, <span style="font-weight: 400;">Clean Out Your Computer Day, Caregivers Day, Lash Day, Home Warranty Day, Women Physicians Day.</span></li>
